 *
 * Author: QueryJ's Template Packaging <version>
 *
 * Filename: <filename>.java
 *
 * Description: <if(description_oneline)><description:{chunk | <chunk>}; separator=""><else><description:{line | <line>}; separator="\n *              "><endif>
